name: Gather Community Plant #016 - Bjorn Calleja
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their rendition of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Bjorn Calleja mainly creates scenes that can be both silly and tragic using an animation process with physical paintings. 

"It all starts with a physical painting, which for me is gestural and a playful release of energy..." - Bjorn Calleja
